lyrics:
Barefoot kid dashing through the streets,
Mud sucking under his nails, it greets.
Tram screeches by, drowning all sound,
Man-made racket, all around.

Morning rush, stray crushed and scattered,
Human herd marching, minds all tattered.
A glance at a familiar face, pig-like and vile,
Adds to the stench of human bile.

Cars honking, time's lost in the fray,
Autumn leaves falling, in disarray.
City sludge, defiled and rotten,
In the chaos, all forgotten.
style: punk kids chorus is singing the song
